<p>As a Product Design Engineer at Google, you will be developing iconic, consumer focused computing devices. You have a solid mechanical and consumer design background, as well as familiarity with system integration and fast-paced consumer development lifecycles. You will be comfortable working in a number of areas- for example defining enclosures, mechanisms, MLB planning, connectors, and modules. You will be expected to work closely with cross functional teams in operations, product, and hardware to define and deliver outstanding products.</p>
